            "question": "Where should I place the Rakaat Counter?",
            "answer": "<p>Place the device on a flat, stable surface near your prayer space, within the sensor’s detection range. It does not need to be held or touched during salah — simply position it before you begin and let it track your prayer naturally.</p>"
